title: Premier League stats: Which unlucky teams have hit the woodwork most in 2016/17?
text:
1 of 21 How many times has your club hit the woodwork so far this season? 
There's nothing more agonising than a whistling shot that rattles the bar late in a game, but some Premier League teams have endured that feeling more than others. 
Arsenal , Liverpool and Manchester City have found the woodwork more than most, though two other top contenders can feel more aggrieved.
